						<summary>

						<p>North wall of the same <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa.</hi></p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">••• ••••• ḷadēva : Year 4[.].</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription is built in at the beginning. So, the name of the king, the date and some other important details are lost.</p>						

						<p>It appears to record a gift of lamp and the undertaking given in this regard by four persons. Neḍuṅguṉṟa-nāḍu, Jayaṅgoṇḍaśōḻa-[maṇḍalam] and [••• •••] Perumpūdūr are mentioned.</p>						

